sequenceDiagram
    participant Index as models-index.yaml<br/>(Local File)
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Output as output/ directory<br/>(Local Filesystem)
    participant Catalog as data/models-catalog.yaml<br/>(Local File)
    participant MCPIdx as mcp-servers-index.yaml<br/>(Local File)
    participant MCPFiles as input/mcp_servers/<br/>(Local Files)
    participant MCPCat as mcp-servers-catalog.yaml<br/>(Local File)
    participant Konflux as Konflux Pipeline<br/>(CI/CD)
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>(Volume Mount)

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Index,Catalog: Flow 1: Model Metadata Extraction & Catalog Generation
        Index->>Extractor: Read models-index.yaml
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections/{id}<br/>Bearer Token (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>Extractor: Collection models list
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{name}<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>Extractor: Model details (downloads, likes, tags)
        Extractor->>HF: GET /{repo}/raw/main/README.md<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>Extractor: README content (YAML frontmatter)

        Extractor->>OCI: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+, Registry Auth
        OCI-->>Extractor: OCI Manifest (model card layer ref)
        Extractor->>OCI: GET /v2/{repo}/blobs/{digest}<br/>TLS 1.2+
        OCI-->>Extractor: Model card content (YAML/markdown)

        Note over Extractor: Enrichment Engine:<br/>Priority: HF YAML > HF API > HF README ><br/>HF Tags > OCI YAML > OCI Regex
        Extractor->>Output: Write metadata.yaml per model
        Extractor->>Output: Write enrichment.yaml (provenance)
        Extractor->>Catalog: Write aggregated models-catalog.yaml
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over MCPIdx,MCPCat: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation
        MCPIdx->>Extractor: Read mcp-servers-index.yaml
        MCPFiles->>Extractor: Read individual server YAML files
        Extractor->>OCI: GET /v2/{mcp-image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+
        OCI-->>Extractor: Image manifest (architectures, timestamps)
        Extractor->>MCPFiles: Write enriched server YAML (idempotent)
        Extractor->>MCPCat: Write mcp-servers-catalog.yaml
    end

    rect rgb(224, 255, 224)
        Note over Konflux,Dashboard: Flow 3: Container Image Build & Consumption
        Note over Konflux: Dockerfile.konflux:<br/>COPY data/*.yaml /app/data/
        Konflux->>Quay: Push odh-model-metadata-collection<br/>HTTPS/443, Registry Push Auth
        Note over Dashboard: Pod mounts container volume
        Dashboard->>Dashboard: Read /app/data/*.yaml<br/>Local filesystem (no network)
    end
